data.title: 1700+ Women Elected to Office
data.meta_description: EMILYs List has helped elect 1700+ Democratic, pro-choice women in our history.
data.text:
Women We’ve Helped Elect

EMILYs List-Endorsed Candidates

EMILYs List wins elections.

EMILYs List wins elections. Since our founding, we have helped elect 175 Democratic pro-choice women to the House, 26 to the Senate, 20 to governors’ seats, and more than 1,500 women to state and local office. EMILYs List has also become one of the largest financial resources for minority women seeking federal office.

Updated February 2023
